<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-50 via-yellow-100 to-yellow-50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <!-- Header -->
  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Introduction -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-lg p-4 md:p-6 shadow-md">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
      <div class="bg-yellow-400 text-blue-800 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg font-bold text-sm md:text-base flex-shrink-0">
        IMPARARE TUTTI con Graf
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-800">
      Quando scrivi può capitare di commettere errori di cui non ti accorgi e che gli altri ti fanno notare.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Table 1: Types of tasks -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-lg p-4 md:p-6 shadow-md">
    <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold text-pink-600 mb-4">
      • Riguarda i tuoi quaderni di classe quarta. In quali tipi di compiti ti è capitato di commetterli più spesso?
    </h3>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full border-collapse border-2 border-cyan-400">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-cyan-100">
            <th class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 text-left font-bold text-cyan-800">Tipo di compito</th>
            <th class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 text-center font-bold text-cyan-800">Mai</th>
            <th class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 text-center font-bold text-cyan-800">A volte</th>
            <th class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 text-center font-bold text-cyan-800">Spesso</th>
            <th class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 text-center font-bold text-cyan-800">Sempre</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 font-medium">Dettato / Copiatura</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 font-medium">Ricerca</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 font-medium">Tema / Scrittura di un testo</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-3 py-3 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Table 2: Types of errors -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-lg p-4 md:p-6 shadow-md">
    <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold text-pink-600 mb-4">
      • E quali tipi di errori ti capita di commettere più spesso?
    </h3>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full border-collapse border-2 border-cyan-400 text-sm md:text-base">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-cyan-100">
            <th class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-3 text-center font-bold text-cyan-800" colspan="2">Tipo di errore</th>
            <th class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-3 text-center font-bold text-cyan-800">Mai</th>
            <th class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-3 text-center font-bold text-cyan-800">A volte</th>
            <th class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-3 text-center font-bold text-cyan-800">Spesso</th>
            <th class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-3 text-center font-bold text-cyan-800">Sempre</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2" colspan="2">Dimenticanza di lettere ("eroporto", invece di "aeroporto")</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2" colspan="2">Aggiunta di lettere ("bissonte" invece di "bisonte")</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2" colspan="2">Inversione di lettere ("matimateca" invece di "matematica")</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 font-medium" rowspan="5">Scrittura errata di suoni difficili</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2">gn/gl</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2">sce/scie, sce/sche, sci/schi</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2">ce/cie, ce/che, ci/chi</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2">ge/gie, ge/ghe, gi/ghi</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2">cu/qu, cqu/qq</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2" colspan="2">H nel verbo avere</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2" colspan="2">Unione o separazione delle parole</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2" colspan="2">Apostrofo / Accento</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2" colspan="2">Doppie</td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
            <td class="border-2 border-cyan-400 px-2 py-2 text-center bg-cyan-50"></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Tips -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-purple-50 rounded-lg p-4 md:p-6 shadow-md border-2 border-pink-300">
    <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-bold text-pink-600 mb-4">
      Ecco due consigli per allenarti a scrivere bene le parole che ti sembrano difficili
    </h3>

    <div class="space-y-4 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="font-bold text-pink-600 flex-shrink-0">1.</span>
        <p>Scrivi con attenzione la parola su un foglio. Osservala dopo averla scritta cercando di "fotografarla con la mente". Chiudi gli occhi e visualizzala: sarà più facile ricordarla.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="font-bold text-pink-600 flex-shrink-0">2.</span>
        <p>Scrivi le parole che per te sono più difficili da ricordare su un apposito quaderno. Così, quando non sei sicura/o di come si scrivono puoi controllare sul tuo quaderno.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise Controls -->
  <div class="mt-6">
    <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls', color: 'pink', show_exercise_buttons: false %>
  </div>
</div>
